    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >觉得《Goat Simulator 3》不能更迷人了？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大错特错！我们新增了 20 件魔法装备，你必将对此兴奋不已。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其中 6 件魔法装备带有能力，还有 1 款全新载具以及 5 种全新本能。听起来超（魔）“杖”，不是吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204290/extras/b01967c65d75ab7a9e496bf1cfa0d053.avif?t=1734005654\" width=616 height=300 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你终于能有个朋友了——虽然是在游戏里</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204290/extras/2bce75474f8624d4c503b2abe1ebf925.poster.avif?t=1734005654\" width=250 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204290/extras/2bce75474f8624d4c503b2abe1ebf925.webm?t=1734005654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204290/extras/2bce75474f8624d4c503b2abe1ebf925.mp4?t=1734005654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >而你肯定会彻底迷上这款全新的载具的</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204290/extras/31d2d5721ce35c25ad59394e9d87b3b9.poster.avif?t=1734005654\" width=250 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204290/extras/31d2d5721ce35c25ad59394e9d87b3b9.webm?t=1734005654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204290/extras/31d2d5721ce35c25ad59394e9d87b3b9.mp4?t=1734005654\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不像其他魔法世界，我们这里欢迎每一个人</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204290/extras/25998c68c6e0602cb5aac8191acfd7e3.poster.avif?t=1734005654\" width=616 height=205 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204290/extras/25998c68c6e0602cb5aac8191acfd7e3.webm?t=1734005654\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >以下是完整的新增内容列表，供那些居然耐心到读到这里还没退出去的玩家查阅</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >–猫头鹰同伴</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >–大锅</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >–水晶球</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >–飞天扫帚</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >–翼龙翅膀</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >–魔法袍</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >–奥数法袍</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >–链锁魂甲</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >–女巫高跟鞋</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >–链锁魂靴</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >–龙鳞</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >–飞奔的毛发</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >–游戏管理员</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >–魔法学校围巾</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >–链锁魂盔</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >–尖尖帽</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >–大号魔术师帽子</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >–女巫帽</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >–龙角</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >–魔杖角</p>",
